title: Yooland Indoor Playground At Westgate: Fun Outer Space
blurb: Yooland Indoor Playground at Westgate offers space play.
description: Yooland Indoor Playground at Westgate is an indoor playground with an outer space theme. It offers a variety of play areas and activities for children of different ages. Kids can explore space-themed play structures, climb through tunnels, and slide down slides. There are also interactive games and activities that encourage learning and development. Yooland Indoor Playground is a great place for families to spend time together and have fun. It is suitable for children aged 2 to 12 years old. Parents can relax and watch their children play in a safe and supervised environment. The playground is designed to promote physical activity, creativity, and social interaction.

title: Yooland Indoor Playground at Westgate, Singapore
blurb: Largest indoor playground in the West with space theme.
description: Yooland at Westgate is the largest indoor playground in the West to-date, featuring an outer space theme. It includes a double-decked indoor play area, an expansive ball pit filled with white, grey and pink coloured balls, a huge funnel slide that simulates a black hole with flashing LED light strips, see-through tunnels and slides, a spiral tube slide, and a wavy LED slide with multiple lanes. There are also interactive games at the ball pit and trampoline area, a ball shooter, trampolines for jumping while shooting balls through the hoop, a brick wall where bricks light up when stacked upon each other, a running wheel, Space Kitchen and Space Supermarket.
